3️⃣ Current Pipeline (June 2025)

✅ A. Data Collection
	•	Script: fetch_raw_trades.py
	•	Pulls raw trade listings from Traderie into:

/data/raw/raw_trades_<mode>.json



✅ B. Unified Extraction & Aggregation
	•	Script: extract_and_aggregate_ist_prices.py
	•	Fully self-contained:
	•	Filters valid rune-to-rune trades.
	•	Rejects:
	•	Non-rune items
	•	Multi-item trades (AND trades)
	•	Invalid quantities
	•	Self-trades (e.g. Ist ⇄ Ist)
	•	Directly computes Ist-normalized prices:
	•	Uses raw trade ratios directly.
	•	No log-space modeling.
	•	Outputs final pricing:

/data/extracted/<mode>_ist_normalized_prices.csv


	•	Includes trade count per rune for confidence scoring.

