4️⃣ Abandoned: Log-Space Price Solver
	•	Early implementation used log-space least squares to solve for all rune prices.
	•	Issues observed:
	•	Global scale drift.
	•	Difficult to debug.
	•	Sensitive to sparse pairwise data.
	•	Fully deprecated in favor of raw trade aggregation.

